    ABOUT US

    Radio Works is home to a locally-owned group of radio stations, featuring homegrown staff who take pride in their careers and love providing for the community. From the on-air staff to the team of marketing specialists, we at Radio Works live by - and believe in - providing the best in music, information, promotion, and personality.

     

    Radio Works provides the best in music choices, in addition to delivering the top information regarding local news, sports, ag reporting, and weather. We also have the latest in online web technology with our Media Works division. We pride ourselves in entertaining our listeners and giving our advertisers great retained audiences from southwest Minnesota and northwest Iowa to the South Dakota border and dipping down to Norfolk, Nebraska.
